                    SkyPartSolutions delivers premium aircraft components to
                    airlines, MROs, and private operators worldwide.
                  </p>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                    Our commitment to quality, safety, and customer satisfaction
                    makes us the preferred choice for aviation parts sourcing.
                  </p>
                  <a
                    href="/about"
                    class="bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
                  >
                    Learn More About Us
                  </a>
